U . S . Commerce ' s Daley arrives in Argentina . U . S . Commerce Secretary William Daley arrived in Argentina Thursday for a three - day official visit during which he will meet President Carlos Menem , Foreign Minister Guido di Tella and Economy Minister Roque Fernandez . Daley made no comments to reporters on his arrival from Belo Horizonte , Brazil , where deputy ministers from across the Americas are drafting an agreement to set up a Free Trade Area of the Americas ( FTAA ) . After lunch with Di Tella , Daley was meeting Fernandez and also planned to hold talks with Menem at 1930 local ( 2230 GMT ) . ( ( - - Buenos Aires Newsroom 541 318 - 0657 ) ) 
